criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient's agreement to participate

          -  Diabetic peripheral neuropathy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Causes of neuropathy other than diabetes

          -  Severe renal disease

          -  Recent treatment for cancer or haematological malignancies;

          -  Presence of foot ulcers;

          -  Peripheral arterial disease ;

          -  Use of agents in the previous 3 months that could interfere with the interpretation of
             results, such as opiates, vitamin B compounds or antioxidants;

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Lactation
